records.name: Holiday Inn Resort Kandooma Maldives - Kids Stay & Eat Free And Dive Free For Certified Divers For A Minimum 3 Nights Stay

descriptions.direction: Located in Kandooma, Holiday Inn Resort Kandooma Maldives by IHG is on a private beach. Kandooma Beach is another place to visit that comes recommended. Take an opportunity to explore the area for water adventures such as parasailing and other activities like whale-watching.
descriptions.general: Embark on a journey to a tropical oasis at Holiday Inn Resort Kandooma Maldives, just a short speedboat ride from Velana International Airport. This all-natural island resort is blessed with lush tropical greenery, clear turquoise waters, and world-class diving and surfing at your doorstep. Our spacious 154 villas offer beach, ocean, garden, or lagoon access, ensuring the epitome of comfort.
